Cloudflare DNS Records
----------------------

    dns-leak-server.phantom.tc    NS      ns-leak-1.phantom.tc
    ns-leak-1.phantom.tc          A       <server IPv4>
    ns-leak-1.phantom.tc          AAAA    <server IPv6>

    All records: DNS only (no proxy).


Worker Integration (check.phantom.tc)
-------------------------------------

    Cloudflare Worker generates HMAC-signed subdomains:

    POST /dns/start (with Turnstile token)
      → Returns array of subdomains

    Client fetches each subdomain:
      → DNS resolve captures resolver IP
      → HTTPS response returns it immediately

    No KV, no polling, no server-to-worker communication.
    Results flow directly: DNS server → HTTPS → client.


Environment Variables (.env)
----------------------------

    DNS_ZONE        Zone name (dns-leak-server.phantom.tc)
    NS_HOST         NS hostname (ns-leak-1.phantom.tc)
    SERVER_IPV4     Server public IPv4 (returned as A record)
    SERVER_IPV6     Server public IPv6 (returned as AAAA record)
    TOKEN_TTL       HMAC token expiry in seconds (default: 30)
    ACME_EMAIL      Let's Encrypt registration email
